&lt;p>Read: &lt;a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3028">http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3028&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>SCP-3028 is a wooden window box planter. Flowering plants grown in SCP-3028 will grow at roughly twenty times their natural rate. Plants grown in SCP-3028, hereby SCP-3028-1, will develop abnormal pigmentation patterns on their leaves and petals beginning at maturity in the form of easily legible English-language political or social commentary that is almost universally considered irrelevant, nonsensical, or objectionable; a sample can be found in Appendix A.&lt;/p>
